flowchart TD
    A[1. Developer push code] --> B[2. SonarScanner membaca source code]
    B --> C[3. Scanner mengirim data ke SonarQube Server]
    C --> D[4. Compute Engine menganalisis - rules + metrics]
    D --> E[5. Hasil disimpan ke Database]
    E --> F[6. Dashboard menampilkan report]
    F --> G{7. Quality Gate}
    G -->|Memenuhi threshold| H[✅ PASS]
    G -->|Tidak memenuhi| I[❌ FAIL]

    style A fill:#E3F2FD,color:#333
    style B fill:#E3F2FD,color:#333
    style C fill:#E3F2FD,color:#333
    style D fill:#FFF3E0,color:#333
    style E fill:#FFF3E0,color:#333
    style F fill:#FFF3E0,color:#333
    style G fill:#F3E5F5,color:#333
    style H fill:#C8E6C9,color:#333
    style I fill:#FFCDD2,color:#333
